title: Sunroom Cafe
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, American, Juice bar, Take-out, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Sunday brunch offers quite a few vegan and vegetarian items, including a tofu scramble, tofu breakfast burrito and tofu heuvos rancheros. The day-to-day menu has fewer choices for vegans and vegetarians, but does have a vegan veggie burger and some vegan pasta/noodle and stir fry dishes.
